  [3]: https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/11/docs/api/java.desktop/javax/swing/JFrame.html#getContentPane()
  [4]: https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/11/docs/api/java.desktop/java/awt/Container.html
  [5]: https://docs.oracle.com/javase/tutorial/uiswing/components/toplevel.html
  [6]: https://docs.oracle.com/javase/tutorial/uiswing/layout/border.html

